{"h68e8310bg1d7bg4c7ag8a70ge8a6080e36e3": ["Watch yerself - there's somethin' rotten in the booze. ", "bb9c82a2-7ed9-45ed-99b6-58f84520fb8c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_Goblin002.html", "3f472c1b-b9bb-5b2a-060f-7b1ad0172687"], "h1ddb7a47g9fc6g41edg8a95g4919b0da29ab": ["Pish. Pure <i>pish</i>. N'ain't even <i>drunk</i>, see?", "bb9c82a2-7ed9-45ed-99b6-58f84520fb8c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_Goblin002.html", "69412584-8d5b-c1fc-81a4-a202e2bbab75"], "hdcb9b640g01dfg4cffgae4fge3f345e10492": ["'Avin' a drink? S'all the sweeter when it's free, innit?", "bb9c82a2-7ed9-45ed-99b6-58f84520fb8c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_Goblin002.html", "d2f473aa-9afe-eda4-24e7-dd18b8c97375"], "h7bd86fadg5c45g4b15g9c40gc7d5d48c1ea1": ["Indeed.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_Goblin002.html", "900110a2-1505-3ad5-fef4-d5275b95fd66"], "h33ceabdeg6161g40a1g8fcfg0a722e269def": ["'Course, sweet piss is still piss. ", "bb9c82a2-7ed9-45ed-99b6-58f84520fb8c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_Goblin002.html", "275ec639-5804-ae9f-c2f7-328aa6911579"], "h3854eacbg3ce8g4f75gb4adgf98a887b5f9e": ["That inn was askin' for a burnin', sellin' this muck. Ain't even <i>chewy</i>.", "bb9c82a2-7ed9-45ed-99b6-58f84520fb8c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_Goblin002.html", "9d1317e1-c4d4-943a-5fb7-7d4f0953bbc8"], "hd54b4ea8ga28eg408bg9f7ag650b05c434ea": ["Free? Where did you get it all?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_Goblin002.html", "b69723ca-528a-a665-4cdf-5c553e88eadc"], "h9bea9cddg7bbfg4d6bg9481gdca7f95d00a7": ["Where the 'ell do you get yours? From an <i>inn</i>, numpty.", "bb9c82a2-7ed9-45ed-99b6-58f84520fb8c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_Goblin002.html", "1920ce41-2356-dfa5-409b-66d115b5904c"], "h1cb46f90g08bag4632g8567gcc3ad75b9c37": ["'Course you won't find much there now. Took all the good stuff afore we burned it.", "bb9c82a2-7ed9-45ed-99b6-58f84520fb8c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_Goblin002.html", "d858370d-2f85-e9e0-8d29-80f6887c8375"], "hddf4a19ag8135g49a7g9269g0b91ff91a863": ["Is it? Looks like swill to me.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_Goblin002.html", "1f0c68f2-1fa7-4fd8-8c40-43f9981e5d13"], "h9250f00eg1d38g4ca5ga286ge3238f493b79": ["Aye, but can't expect proper stuff from them fancy inns, can ya?", "bb9c82a2-7ed9-45ed-99b6-58f84520fb8c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_Goblin002.html", "6a38359d-8467-e6b4-91d0-d193ccca730d"], "hc0584b1dg1fb9g44a5g8f5fg36c13b597500": ["I swear, I got more dizzy from the smoke when we burnt the place down.", "bb9c82a2-7ed9-45ed-99b6-58f84520fb8c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_Goblin002.html", "43f0ea40-5c5b-07fe-eb61-2ca7c1a43b7f"], "h226dc15dg1a32g4911g9c00gd32ffb82b87f": ["I'd rather drink drider-venom.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_Goblin002.html", "4956b024-9adb-967f-935a-5832c2eb5531"], "h8f2cec49g6e16g448fg9d39g586428507bae": ["That some fancy elf brew, is it? Never know, might 'ave it.", "bb9c82a2-7ed9-45ed-99b6-58f84520fb8c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_Goblin002.html", "63230cbb-f15f-2729-0b07-f3e818c467a2"], "h4928ea54g8002g43deg8f8fg4223d8c66107": ["We lifted all sorts from that inn afore we burned it.", "bb9c82a2-7ed9-45ed-99b6-58f84520fb8c", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Festivities_Goblin002.html", "aa43a44c-e7aa-b70e-f956-b8455a1aae07"]}